  "detailed_description": "This game is a cute kitten reflex click game☆<br />\r\nYou can see the content singly by clicking.<br />\r\nWhen an enemy appears, please click on the enemy in a hurry.<br />\r\nIf you don't click quickly, the enemy will run away.<br />\r\nCan kittens protect their homes?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere are no levels or ranks.<br />\r\nThere is one ending.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhen a game is cleared, a special mode comes out.<br />\r\nIt's also most suitable for practice of the child's small mouse.",
